# Worktree contents are never committed (see WORKFLOW.md) — git worktree add creates them on demand
**/worktrees/
# Exception: the PoP ROOT worktrees/ folder exists versioned (it hosts the vault work of parallel agents); only its contents are ignored — see worktrees/.gitignore
!/worktrees/
/worktrees/*
!/worktrees/.gitignore

# Clones of aggregated repositories (keep in sync with "Aggregated repositories" in INDEX.md)
# `included` projects with a repo: categories/<category>/<project>/
# Example: categories/applications/my-app/

# Obsidian local state (remove this if you prefer to version your workspace)
.obsidian/

# Python bytecode from scripts/
__pycache__/
